episodes.title: Explained: How Prince Andrew’s Epstein Scandal Led King Charles to Strip His Royal Titles
episodes.description:
Prince Andrew, the younger brother of King Charles III, has been stripped of his royal titles and evicted from his Windsor residence amid renewed pressure over his alleged ties to convicted sex offender Jeffrey Epstein. Once known as the Duke of York, Andrew will now be called Andrew Mountbatten-Windsor. This video breaks down who Prince Andrew is, his royal and military background, the timeline of his association with Epstein, the sexual abuse allegations against him, and how it led to this unprecedented decision by the King.
